description: Our Outdoor Commercial Furniture range features durable hard wearing rattan furniture, aluminium tables & chairs and comfortable cafe bistro seating. Our outdoor furniture provides exceptional value for money and can be used for a variety of outdoor commercial applications. Many are available from stock for fast delivery. All items which contain foam and/or fabric are CRIB 5 Certified unless otherwise stated.
